Þat var eitt sumar, 
at Grímr bjó för sína í Vík austr 
eptir Harald dauðan, mág sinn, 
fyrir því athann átti  þar miklar eignir.

<bl id="000004436342219936342592692857" data-link-target="properties-57" data-link-iri="properties/alignments/projects~57" data-link-value="siehe"><ini id="000004436342334950231481521590">Þ</ini>at <chr id="000004436342339388888888943282">v</chr>ar eitt <kap id="000004436342344737268518577048">s</kap>umar, <z id="000004436342244850694444419672" data-link-target="properties-78" data-link-iri="properties/linebindings/projects~78" data-link-value="Zeile" /><nl />at <vsl id="000004436342331244212963000975">G</vsl>rímr bjó för sína í V<all id="000004436342356430555555639778" data-link-target="properties-66" data-link-iri="properties/ligatures/projects~66" data-link-value="Buchstabenverbindung 1 ">í</all>k austr <vz id="000004436342252387731481570820" data-link-target="properties-82" data-link-iri="properties/indentations/projects~82" data-link-value="Verszeilenumbruch 2a" /><nl />eptir <sup id="000004436342367437500000062286" data-link-target="" data-link-iri="" data-link-value="Hochgestellt in der Transkription">Harald</sup> dau<wtr id="000004436342265232638888919263" data-link-target="properties-90" data-link-iri="properties/wordseparators/projects~90" data-link-value="Worttrenner 1 › siehe" />ðan, <insec id="000004436342370581018518576494">mág </insec>sinn, <spatium_v id="000004436342271391203703738522" width="1" /><nl />fyrir því <add id="000004436342304277777777828084">at</add><oms id="000004436342299424768518527263">hann</oms> <oms id="000004436342296030092592678988">átti </oms> <cpl id="000004436342291663194444404939">þar</cpl> m<del id="000004436342276410879629645922" num_sign="0" />iklar eignir.</bl><nl />

Grímr unni henni mikit, ok lætr hann þat eptir henni. 
Hún var hverri konu vænni ok betr at sér um alla hluti,
 þeira er í Noregi váru. 
Þeira för var búin virðuliga.

<bl id="000004436342493348379629644802" data-link-target="properties-61" data-link-iri="properties/alignments/projects~61" data-link-value="Bereich 1a"><ini id="000004436342606019675925920222">G</ini>rímr <vsl id="000004436342597724537037066064">u</vsl>nni <chr id="000004436342610309027777859800">h</chr>enni <kap id="000004436342614041666666773306">m</kap>ikit, ok l<all id="000004436342619626157407418054" data-link-target="properties-64" data-link-iri="properties/ligatures/projects~64" data-link-value="Buchstabenverbindung 2a">æ</all>tr <oms id="000004436342575649305555631787">hann</oms> þat <sup id="000004436342629741898148160649" data-link-target="" data-link-iri="" data-link-value="Hochgestellt in der Transkription">eptir</sup> henni. <z id="000004436342516953703703748996" data-link-target="properties-80" data-link-iri="properties/linebindings/projects~80" data-link-value="Zeilenumbruch 1 " /><nl />Hún <add id="000004436342582651620370456862">var hverri </add>konu vænni<spatium_v id="000004436342550361111111153956" width="1" /> ok betr<del id="000004436342558008101851960179" num_sign="0" /> at sér <cpl id="000004436342570162037037096209">um</cpl> alla hluti,<vz id="000004436342523789351851958494" data-link-target="properties-84" data-link-iri="properties/indentations/projects~84" data-link-value="Verszeile" /><nl /> þeira<abr id="000004436342590993055555669897" data-link-target="" data-link-iri="" data-link-value="Abkürzung"> er</abr> í Nor<wtr id="000004436342540800925925924686" data-link-target="properties-88" data-link-iri="properties/wordseparators/projects~88" data-link-value="Worttrenner 2 › Worttrenner 2a" />egi váru. <nl />Þeira för var búin <insec id="000004436342633575231481531016">virðuliga</insec>.</bl>
